snippet.title: Disney Dreamlight Valley – Sew Delightful Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Help Sally settle into the Valley! Her spider messengers have spun a web of mysteries and only you can help Sally from Disney Tim Burton’s The Nightmare Before Christmas become the Valley’s newest Villager.

Embark on new Friendship Quests, help Sally set up the perfect macabre date night, embrace the art of quilting, and puzzle out her latest premonitions… Could they spell trouble?

Play Disney Dreamlight Valley now https://disneydreamlightvalley.com/getnow 
Learn more about the Sew Delightful update: https://disneydreamlightvalley.com/news/SewDelightfulUpdate
